Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？月影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强还好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  竟然还有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  烈火你快逃  这里交给我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已经无希望得救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能连累你也死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也死在这里的话  谁来阻止它们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是红莲的年轻队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负有打倒妖魔的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们红莲是为了打倒妖魔而召集的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直属于将军大人的退魔机构
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也死在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁人来阻止他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒在河边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我费了好大的功夫才把你运来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有下毒的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人跑到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开她  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟月影最先注意的就是这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这里频频发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是妖魔所作的杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了收拾这些妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们预计跟分散的红莲众会合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影应该有能力逃出那个困境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与同伴一起等待我抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我渺小的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你还有脸到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只月影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连救自己的女孩子都让她被妖魔掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不敢相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  你说太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火想念月影的心是不下于我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我当然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无言反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候被红莲带走的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得战斗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只晓得学习战斗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每天持续的辛苦修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常关心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持我们的人是月影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与小茜突然的语言冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的心更加沉痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林走着走着它就突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没命的逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它  抢走我们村子姑娘的肯定是它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想沮丧到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次救了你的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能被关在那个鬼地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  也许还来得及  我们赶快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个村里的人说的  应该是这个附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小屋很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起冲进去速战速决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太冒险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打不过的话怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还有同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有天受到黑漆漆的家伙攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑漆漆的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就只剩下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不努力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会没人保护森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要连不在的同伴的份也努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计我们的想法都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不害人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙毕竟还是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个鬼放在这地方  真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁晓得它何时会露出鬼的本性来袭击人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是长成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村人看到我就怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会长角呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样一直笑着是不是就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那些会绑架村里姑娘的鬼是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那个鬼在哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这前方有片竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个鬼就在竹林深处的洞窟里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我就招待你们吃森林里的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  为何不杀那个鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有做什么坏事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且烈火你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀  就算是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不加害于人  就不是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尽量避免无意义的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有必须打倒的恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从那洞窟传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我们应付就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要裂开了  我快坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快坏掉了  快坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在倒在我脚下的这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是在这惨状之中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的睡容就像普通女孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是由于拥有特殊力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不惜伪装自己的外貌  自己一个人隐居起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天真无邪的表情下面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知存在着多少黑暗的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小遥啊  真辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无处可去的话  跟我们一起如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  这只狗干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  这是你捡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想办法管它呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好怕  好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要凑近那么臭的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩乃姐  这只狗是雌还是雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这只笨狗的行动  就知道不是雌的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么笨狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  有取好名字了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做千代丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么土气的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我只是试着这么喊喊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  千代丸这名字太没品味了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你说什么名字才有品味？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如叫小白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一点都不白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他红豆怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是安大哥的安（同音）  是指红豆面包的红豆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢吃红豆面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家一起喊名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那只狗有反应的名字怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  那就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在讨论你的事  你还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫千代丸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着觉  可以进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  刚才你为什么不告诉大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟常人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我自己也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己为什么变成那个样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内可能流着…丑陋的妖魔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们确实是被组织起来打鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见得所有的鬼都是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥  你是为了被惨杀的村中少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身对抗恶鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用太在意大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对我来说  你还是救命恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家找我一起走的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就更难过  自己有事隐瞒大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙出现之前  我都还是过得很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们夺走了我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友  父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说有点不妥  应该说是我已记不起他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你救了我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被另一位女性救了一命的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是红莲的首领收留我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身都是伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奄奄一息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影不眠不休照顾我  才救回我的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后  不论做什么事我们都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把我当亲弟弟一样疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时又像疼爱自己的子女一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在红莲的辛苦修行  对我来说并不苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有她在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对失去记忆的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我唯一能倾心相诉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到月影对你这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后换我来保护烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让鬼杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我过言了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  烈火你有月影…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是肮脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内有鬼的血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里很脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  很脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行  别做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…我是肮脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  我这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好怪  自己好不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.07,0:24:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.74,0:24:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.12,0:24:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体中心好热
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪  我变得好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.98,0:25:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.58,0:25:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.73,0:25:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪边呀  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.07,0:25:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看就知道了  我们在打鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是以多欺小欺负没抵抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.69,0:26:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.76,0:26:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿这些来想请小哥你们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我果然是不应该来人类居住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.57,0:26:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  给你带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.97,0:26:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.11,0:26:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太没用了  红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.71,0:26:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还放鬼逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.78,0:26:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.18,0:26:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.39,0:26:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影舞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负有打鬼的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑刚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.60,0:26:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪你们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.80,0:26:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟你们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老大的直属部下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.47,0:26:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲与我们负责间谍活动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.07,0:26:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只拥有调查事件到解决事件之间的权限
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.68,0:26:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而黑刚则是完全的杀鬼部队
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.15,0:27:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的战斗力  恐怕还在红莲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙我们带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿他怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.56,0:27:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我打到的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么处置与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.76,0:27:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.43,0:27:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
